-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deep_Thought&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deep_Thought_%28chess_computer%29\">Deep Thought from Wikipedia</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.computerhistory.org/chess/challenging-the-world-champion/\">Challenging the World Champion | Mastering the Game</a> <a href=\"/The_Computer_History_Museum\" title=\"The Computer History Museum\">The Computer History Museum</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.game-ai-forum.org/icga-tournaments/program.php?id=349\">Deep Thought's ICGA Tournaments</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/player/deep_thought.html\">Deep Thought's games from chessgames.com</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tim-mann.org/deepthought.html\">Deep Thought from Tim Mann's Chess Pages</a></li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tim-mann.org/DT_eval_tune.tar.gz\">Source code to tune Deep Thought's evaluation</a> in tar.gz format.</dd>\n<dd> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.tim-mann.org/DT_eval_tune.txt\">Andreas Nowatzyk's explanations of the the source code</a></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Deep_Thought&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"re